{"tid":1481404,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(黑暗兵法) 對付d自私既藍絲","createTime":"2019-08-17T16:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T03:48:56.000Z","uid":56618,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e953e2d7e0d2395204b3735dbadc797f85421d36","tid":1481404,"uid":56618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"眾所周知<br />\n藍絲係唔會認佢地係收錢出黎既<br />\n既然係咁 我地就好應該利用依一點<br />\n<br />\n發夢諗到popo有臥底<br />\n點解示威者唔可以有臥底<br />\n如果坊間突然出現左好多唔存在既蛇頭<br />\n資助藍絲行出黎<br />\n會發生咩事咩<br />\n<br />\n首先 因為假蛇頭係無諗過比錢既 咁個車馬費就可以越開越高 惡性競爭之下 真蛇頭都要比更多既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次 出到黎既藍絲收唔到錢 又搵唔到蛇頭拎裝備物資 佢地唯有轉身走人 成功減少藍絲示威人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三 吸取過教訓既佢地 會懷疑其他蛇頭 而重點係依樣野係無得證明 又唔會上報紙 咁就減少左佢地再出去既機會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 可以製作相關黑暗文宣黎勸身邊既藍絲 小心比人呃左出去 令佢地內部出現信任危機<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補充 請用無辦法查實既方法去聯絡人 倒如tg 假既微信<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd7579b74be916024075f7980dcc2d26ac03462","tid":1481404,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:52:25.000Z","msg":"818維園見！所有聽日去嘅人都同我入一入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc37d96bfea8ddd3b59e6bf35e5f5fdc7916355e","tid":1481404,